data.description: With a little bit of love this amazing Gated, Single story Valley Center View will take your breath away. Enjoy beautiful sunrise and sunsets on 2 acres.   The large kitchen features a bay window with views toward the sunrise, an abundance of crisp, white cabinetry and counter space, a double oven and gas cooktop.   Relax in the pool and enjoy the amazing California sunsets! Ejoy the mini Orchard with a variety of fruit trees and ample space for your garden.  The three car garage will store all your toys and cars while providing extra storage space too. You really need to see it to appreciate all the amazing features this home has to offer!
